data.description: **ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN WITH A 3.25% INTEREST RAT. ASK ME HOW***CONVENTIONAL BUYERS this home qualifies for a community program that will give you a reduced interest rate and mortgage insurance saving you $$$*****  Welcome home to 136 N Nebraska Street! This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, RV PARKING, a large backyard perfect for entertaining, an air conditioned shed in the back, no HOA, and LOW TAXES! As you enter the home you'll find high vaulted ceilings, lots of natural light in the great room and a full bedroom and bathroom downstairs. The kitchen has tons of windows that give you a perfect view of your backyard. As you work your way up to the second floor you'll find 3 additional bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The backyard is perfect for entertaining with a patio cover, fully landscaped, mature fruit trees for added privacy, and a bonus room in the back. Not only do you have a large backyard with this home but you also have the convenience of having a large side yard that offers RV parking and the front of the home has a large driveway perfect for a large family or for having guests over. You will also love the location of this home! It's within minutes of the schools and parks. This home has so much potential it is a must see!
